description: This header file declares the API for the CCSP CWMP Helper Container Object, including creation, removal, enrollment, and initialization functions.

methods.name: CcspCwmpCreateHelperContainer
methods.description: Creates a helper container object for CCSP CWMP protocol.

methods.name: CcspCwmpHcoCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the CCSP CWMP Helper Container Object.

methods.name: CcspCwmpHcoRemove
methods.description: Removes the specified CCSP CWMP Helper Container Object.

methods.name: CcspCwmpHcoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary objects into the CCSP CWMP Helper Container.

methods.name: CcspCwmpHcoInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the CCSP CWMP Helper Container Object.
